# Write a program for converting US dollars (USD) into Bulgarian levs (BGN). Use a fixed exchange rate between the dollar and the lev: 1 USD = 1.79549 BGN.
# Guidelines
# ⦁ Read the input from the console (US dollars):
# ⦁ Create a new variable in which you will convert from US dollars to Bulgarian levs, knowing the exchange rate:
# ⦁ Print the received Bulgarian levs.

usd = float(input())
bgn = usd * 1.79549

print(bgn)
